CompMethod.MethodText: Data Reviewer's Guide for details regarding the derivation of this variable.

CompMethod.MethodName: Algorithm to derive all Study Day variables
CompMethod.MethodText: --DY is computed as: --DTC - RFSTDTC + 1 if --DTC is on or after RFSTDTC, --DTC - RFSTDTC if --DTC precedes RFSTDTC.

CompMethod.MethodName: Algorithm to derive all Sequence Numbers
CompMethod.MethodText: --SEQ is computed as: Within all records with the same USUBJID, assigned as 1 for the first record and incremented by 1 for each subsequent record (applied to dataset sorted by key variables). Reset to 1 for each new USUBJID.
Concatenation of protocol number (without character prefix) country, center and subject with leading zeroes.
Internally derived by the electronic data collection software.
